dialog.body: Hello, thank you for contacting Old Stone Auto Insurance. My name is Christian Hughes. May I please have your name?
Hi Christian, my name is Carol Morgan.
Great to meet you, Carol. Can I have the make and model of your vehicle that was involved in the incident?
Yes, it's a two zero one seven Honda Civic.
Thank you, Carol. Could you please provide me with the date of the accident using numbers?
The accident happened on zero eight two zero two two one.
Got it, thank you. Now, could you confirm the address where the incident took place so we can document the claim properly?
The address is one two three Main Street, Cityville.
Thank you for providing that information, Carol. Is there anything else you would like to add before we proceed?
No, that's all for now. Thank you, Christian.
You're welcome, Carol. Thank you for reaching out. We will process your claim accordingly. Have a great day!
